<h3>Book Specifications</h3>
The book was designed to be read as a printed book. While the electronic version is readable on the Kindle 3 and the iPad, the two-column layout will not be great for reading on a small screen.
<ul>
<li/>Paperback: 8x10 Perfect bound format, 152 full color pages. ISBN-10: 1456331655 ISBN-13: 978-1456331658
<li/>E-book: 11MB PDF. You <b>must</b> be willing to use a <a href="http://www.dropbox.com">Dropbox</a> in order to download this book! You will be asked to create one if you do not have one.
</ul>

