<h2>Author's Biography</h2>

Piaw Na has been cycle touring since 1993. He has led independent
trips in his home state of California, and led small groups to many
foreign destinations including Switzerland, Germany, Scotland, Italy,
Austria, France, and
Japan. He has participated in organized tours and self-organized trips
in New Hampshire, Maine, Vermont, and Colorado. He has
taught <a href="http://piaw.blogspot.com/2008/01/bicycle-wheel.html">wheel
building classes</a> multiple times, and is a League Cycling
Instructor
(<a href="http://www.bikeleague.org/cogs/programs/education/instructor_detail/897">license
#1040</a>). Visit his tour reports at <a href="http://touring.piaw.net">http://touring.piaw.net</a>.

